dc_description_s: This data represents General Zoning for Lincoln County, Wisconsin in 2020. [This publication level, polygon feature class provides a graphical representation adn attributation of Zoning in Lincoln County, Wisconsin. Polygons are derived from the tax parcels in the production world that are attributed with the appropriate county Zoning.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://maps.co.lincoln.wi.us/webapps/gisportal/data.html
